n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=5edc817f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"498894702e37446ce53ee909260bec98752ddd2f","tid":2032571,"uid":108006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"你以為隔離病房好似公廁咁自出自入?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45215a88ca69a171ed3daf98adf0604cd6b7cec3","tid":2032571,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vBLp_FzxoNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvBLp_FzxoNo&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=3bb75a55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vBLp_FzxoNo</a>"},{"pid":"de458b770a4e1c7374e11a9decaf6a0ceb7e5762","tid":2032571,"uid":69544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"點解到今時今日，樓主仲係想靠其他人做"},{"pid":"844b0541d10e0871c856a798ff38a367cef01779","tid":2032571,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de458b770a4e1c7374e11a9decaf6a0ceb7e5762","tid":20